name: Deep river
description:
Una corriente incontrolable
que te arrastra, te pule, te modifica.
Desmembrando tus ramas caídas, llevándose a su paso tu antiguo yo.
Para que una nueva forma surja
------------------------------------------
An uncontrollable current
that drags you, polishes you, modifies you.
Dismembering your fallen branches, taking your old self in its wake.
For a new way to emerge
